00:06:07,234 --> 00:06:13,441
We must win, so that this
work for the citizens can start.

71
00:06:15,209 --> 00:06:23,581
Lee Shin Jeok, you mustn't disappoint me.

72
00:06:23,581 --> 00:06:26,553
No matter what.

73
00:06:34,929 --> 00:06:39,133
<i>Hand over Jeong Gi Joon.</i>

74
00:06:39,133 --> 00:06:45,272
<i>Then that would be the base
of trust you yourself create, no?</i>

75
00:06:46,574 --> 00:06:52,113
