115
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:13,319
We must find a way to get out.

116
00:09:13,319 --> 00:09:18,500
No matter how, we must complete our mission.

117
00:09:19,783 --> 00:09:20,619
What?

118
00:09:20,619 --> 00:09:21,456
Daeseong Mountain?

119
00:09:21,456 --> 00:09:22,887
Yes, Rabbit Rock.

120
00:09:22,887 --> 00:09:25,952
Chae Yoon and Cho Tak
are already on their way there.

121
00:09:25,952 --> 00:09:27,004
Is this accurate information?

122
00:09:27,004 --> 00:09:28,576
Yes, it's accurate!

123
00:09:28,576 --> 00:09:34,542
Hence, please prepare so that the royal guard troop
can move at once as soon as the contact comes.

124
00:09:35,403 --> 00:09:36,346
I got it.

125
00:09:36,346 --> 00:09:40,743
You two take the first team of Palace Guard and prepare
so that Chae Yoon's message can come without fail.

126
00:09:40,743 --> 00:09:42,135
Yes.

127
00:09:45,884 --> 00:09:48,220
Their location is finally identified?

128
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:49,149
Yes.

129
00:09:49,149 --> 00:09:53,489
Once their exact location is verified,
he will send a message to us.

130
00:09:56,967 --> 00:09:58,691
Chae Yoon.

131
00:09:59,498 --> 00:10:02,731
You must find So Yi.

132
00:10:03,632 --> 00:10:05,982
You must.

133
00:10:06,464 --> 00:10:08,141
<i>Yes, Your Majesty.</i>

134
00:10:08,438 --> 00:10:12,541
<i>I will return for sure.</i>

135
00:10:14,810 --> 00:10:19,356
<i>Since you need to leave tomorrow,
hurry and see to the preparation.</i>

136
00:10:36,465 --> 00:10:40,045
<i>You should bow when
you return. What is this?</i>

137
00:10:44,343 --> 00:10:46,308
<i>Your Majesty.</i>

138
00:10:46,608 --> 00:10:49,173
<i>Your Majesty said,</i>

139
00:10:49,173 --> 00:10:52,013
<i>the promise to Kang Chae Yoon...</i>

140
00:10:53,615 --> 00:10:58,761
<i>Yes, after this work is done, leave
with that punk who has no manners.</i>

141
00:10:59,121 --> 00:11:07,166
<i>Though I can't pull out a fortune for you,
I'll put together enough gold for a house.</i>

142
00:11:10,745 --> 00:11:14,852
<i>I just hope that punk
won't make you go hungry.</i>

143
00:11:18,817 --> 00:11:20,680
<i>Your Majesty.</i>

144
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:46,779
<i>So Yi.</i>

145
00:11:49,744 --> 00:11:52,074
<i>Thank you.</i>

146
00:11:54,088 --> 00:11:56,278
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

147
00:11:59,754 --> 00:12:04,148
<i>Though it's true I wish
for you to be at my side,</i>

148
00:12:05,798 --> 00:12:13,575
<i>it seems I will get to
breathe at last once you leave.</i>

149
00:12:16,465 --> 00:12:19,998
<i>Isn't that true for you as well?</i>

150
00:12:24,106 --> 00:12:27,243
<i>Day by day,</i>

151
00:12:27,643 --> 00:12:30,744
<i>you must live in joy.</i>

152
00:12:30,744 --> 00:12:33,014
<i>Together with Kang Chae Yoon.</i>

153
00:12:36,208 --> 00:12:39,015
<i>Promise me.</i>

154
00:12:55,134 --> 00:13:03,141
<i>Your Majesty.
I will surely keep my promise to you.</i>

155
00:13:05,202 --> 00:13:11,221
<i>There must be a way.
There has to be. Surely.</i>

156
00:13:15,767 --> 00:13:17,560
What?

157
00:13:17,926 --> 00:13:19,675
Why did you bring the kid here?

158
00:13:19,675 --> 00:13:24,090
She was in danger because of me.

159
00:13:24,375 --> 00:13:27,572
There was... someone chasing us.

160
00:13:27,572 --> 00:13:29,681
How much danger
could the kid be in!?

161
00:13:29,681 --> 00:13:31,273
To bring the kid here
under the situation?

162
00:13:31,273 --> 00:13:33,861
Just leave it be.

163
00:13:44,753 --> 00:13:47,456
Instead of Gaepayi
going out to see her,

164
00:13:47,456 --> 00:13:50,858
it is better that Yeon Doo is here.

165
00:13:50,858 --> 00:13:52,855
You did well to bring her here.

166
00:14:00,053 --> 00:14:02,268
As everyone here knows,

167
00:14:02,268 --> 00:14:06,440
I've conveyed all of
my intentions last time.

168
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:10,979
I will acknolwedge Milbon as
a political party and accept them.

169
00:14:10,979 --> 00:14:15,889
I said, "come to the court
before the day of promulgation."

170
00:14:16,425 --> 00:14:21,415
However, no one has yet come.

171
00:14:21,665 --> 00:14:26,161
Hence, I will now make
my final proposition.

172
00:14:30,532 --> 00:14:34,970
Promulgation of the letters...
on the sanghan (first ten days) of the 9th month.

173
00:14:35,349 --> 00:14:38,940
Amidst the gaze of ten
thousand citizens, I will carry it out.

174
00:14:42,511 --> 00:14:43,612
Your Majesty!

175
00:14:43,612 --> 00:14:48,550
The Ministry of Personnel is to install Eonmun
(Hangul book) and Jeongeum (Hangul typeset) Bureau.

176
00:14:49,769 --> 00:14:54,559
And the Ministry of Rites is to
adopt the letters into the civil exams.

177
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:56,124
Make preparations to carry it out.

178
00:14:56,124 --> 00:14:59,294
Your Majesty, it mustn't!

179
00:14:59,294 --> 00:15:02,230
Yes, it can't!

180
00:15:02,230 --> 00:15:05,634
It cannot be!

181
00:15:08,437 --> 00:15:11,707
But why is everyone like this?

182
00:15:11,707 --> 00:15:17,078
