a proposition, didn't I?

183
00:15:18,113 --> 00:15:20,348
What kind of a nation is Joseon?

184
00:15:20,348 --> 00:15:27,389
Is it a nation where a monarch's pressing of
independant threats are automatically carried out?

185
00:15:27,389 --> 00:15:32,327
Joseon undoubtedly has
a system of State Council.

186
00:15:32,327 --> 00:15:40,468
Hence what I have proposed just needs
to be determined by the State Council.

187
00:15:40,802 --> 00:15:46,147
Just as I mentioned, the Ministry of Personnel
and the Ministry of Rites prepare to carry it out,

188
00:15:46,147 --> 00:15:51,155
and submit their plans to the State Council, and the
three high councilors can discuss matters thoroughly,

189
00:15:51,155 --> 00:15:53,575
and then determine a yes or no.

190
00:15:54,492 --> 00:15:59,754
And I will make the decree
in accordance with their decision,

191
00:16:00,255 --> 00:16:04,226
Hence, the most important event
of the promulgation of the letters,

192
00:16:04,226 --> 00:16:07,629
rests on the approval
of the three state councilors.

193
00:16:07,729 --> 00:16:11,066
Your Majesty!
That is still not permissible!

194
00:16:11,066 --> 00:16:13,468
If you insist on the promulgation of letters...

195
00:16:13,468 --> 00:16:15,103
Look here!

196
00:16:15,103 --> 00:16:20,375
Didn't His Majesty just order the three state
councilors to make the decision after discussing it?

197
00:16:20,375 --> 00:16:24,579
Hence, you just need to wait for the decision
by the State Council, Deputy Chief Scholar.

198
00:16:35,991 --> 00:16:41,029
<i>Is that your answer to last night?</i>

199
00:16:41,363 --> 00:16:45,734
<i>I haven't made a decision yet.</i>

200
00:16:45,867 --> 00:16:50,338
<i>It just means I will put effort in it.</i>

201
00:16:54,653 --> 00:16:57,145
Your Majesty.

202
00:16:57,446 --> 00:17:01,016
Do you think we will receive the approval
from the three state councilors?

203
00:17:03,118 --> 00:17:05,053
I'm not sure.

204
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:09,958
Now we've done our best,
so we await God's disposition, no?

205
00:17:12,694 --> 00:17:18,099
You guys work toward persuading
just one more if possible.

206
00:17:18,099 --> 00:17:19,768
Yes.

207
00:17:20,769 --> 00:17:27,276
Speeding up the Dong-guk-jeong-woon
[instructions of phonological structure of Chinese characters]
will be an asset in persuading the aristocrats.

208
00:17:27,276 --> 00:17:28,452
Yes.

